{"tid":208154,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"（集思廣益）台北台中好去處","createTime":"2017-04-19T10:49:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-19T16:14:12.000Z","uid":40845,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a5a7fc6270c61107a5c6318541e87bd57ca870e1","tid":208154,"uid":40845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T10:49:18.000Z","msg":"下星期會同女朋友去八日台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，基本行程已經有，就係女朋友陪我去曬台北台中所有網上搵到既博物館<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，跟住就係藥妝店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n除左呢o的景點，大家有冇話有咩冷門，但自己覺得幾好既地方或食店，如果有可以留言，感謝大家既付出，小弟沒齒難望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ea6749889a4ea61de985c08fc1d28fa30dbf606","tid":208154,"uid":40845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T10:49:52.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b368c887eafd0d777b4b8baf49b60f94ccdf562","tid":208154,"uid":40845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T10:50:18.000Z","msg":"再推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e20f8fdca5c72554eaf38f346e75a46da98abba","tid":208154,"uid":77445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T10:50:58.000Z","msg":"遲啲都會去台灣玩7日，幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6795f753b8fff9d5e6ee974e26b7977237c93bc","tid":208154,"uid":27397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T10:51:35.000Z","msg":"酒店"},{"pid":"319d1227ac178007f9dd9f41a7c3bd425b68877e","tid":208154,"uid"