moji\" />"},{"pid":"9449da5d80069115d96c5a311c9a72557118af0b","tid":208154,"uid":53676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T12:37:47.000Z","msg":"最好買定清涼茶包過去 再唔係飲佢地既分解茶<br />\n食足咁多日包你唔想再食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09dfe42d72b5fff9ffe24c629fb7c0fb4cc2d0f4","tid":208154,"uid":40845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T14:45:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最緊要買定正露丸/保濟丸<br />\n係台灣掃夜市小食同正常meal都係必備既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你唔講我都唔知，多謝，我會買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁其實係保濟丸定正露丸好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n細細個睇廣告，保濟丸好似柯嘔肚痛食濟都0岩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25413751c20feed480471ec1ab1414b2eb8de7d2","tid":208154,"uid":40845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T14:46:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最好買定清涼茶包過去 再唔係飲佢地既分解茶<br />\n食足咁多日包你唔想再食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n分解茶即係咩來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係7仔買定台灣有類似香港既涼茶鋪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c20bb798e7ea5e2518381b9a95f4867732ffaf0","tid":208154,"uid":44025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T16:14:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>中正記念堂個交接表演真心正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係幾點有？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n晏晝1點-5點每個鐘一次<br />\n6點有降旗睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}